Call AS_PAYBAN(VALEUR) From SUBBIC2
If mkstat=2
 [M]PAYBAN(INDIC) = VALEUR
 Affzo PAYBAN(INDIC) : mkstat = 2
Endif
Onkey 129 Titled GBOUT1 Call B1_PAYBAN(zc) From W2ZBIC1
Onkey   2 Titled GBOUTS Call S_PAYBAN(zc) From W2ZBIC1
Onkey 144 Titled GBOUTP Call P_PAYBAN(zc) From W2ZBIC1
Onkey 146 Titled GBOUTA Call SA_PAYBAN(zc) From W2ZBIC1
